 and death. And so they would....::<br>
<br>
::Those silvery-golden eyes were closed and her soul, as Dawn's, was trapped within one of two pieces of a split locket. Her own piece was locked around Veyriean's neck, on it's way to her home, to Themiscrya. She would no longer sing, play that runic flute, smirk, laugh... She would no longer be, yet she was there, always::<br>
<br>
::Laying beside her Athelfi, a true smile graced those pale lips, her wounded side untended since the war had ended only days before. She had lived a life filled with regret for a past she could not mend, and pain for a legacy she was condemned for. Yet she died with a smile, her first true smile in so many decades, so many centuries. Her age had never been determined, or told of, but she was older than any deserved to be living on the soils of earth. But she was happy in death. Perhaps now her soul could rest and, in time, she could start anew in another place::<br>
<br>
::The small silver flute, adorned with runes, lay in her open palm, her runic sword strapped across her still back. Those runes would glow no more, and, once touched by other hands, would wash away until a day would come when she might hold it again, as something, someone else. That sword was forever hers::<br>
<br>
::And so Sartha Anne Rose lay in her final rest, death's kind hand leading her on into something she had needed for all too long: A new beginning:: <p>~The old days are gone. You can't live in the past, and you can't wait for the future. Now is all we have. You do the other two, you waste your life...
Sartha Anne Rose... Amazon for all time~</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#993300>- </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite>Amazons Unite</a><font color=#993300> - </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya>Sisters of Themiscrya</a> <font color=#993300> - </font><a href="http://www.amazonsunite.i-p.com">Home</a><font color=#993300> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.4 b8<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  